{"tid":1594673,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[國際戰線] 一人一信俾邵逸夫獎得獎人 呼籲佢哋公開放棄得獎！","createTime":"2019-09-25T16:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T17:02:10.000Z","uid":108725,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4448758ba2ec150e760fc05da3659a3e025f7b","tid":1594673,"uid":108725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:15:12.000Z","msg":"今年香港風雨飄搖之際，邵逸夫獎今晚仲歌舞昇平咁搞頒獎典禮，俾條柒婆上去頒獎！邵逸夫獎嘅認受性近年來每況愈下，已經淪落到同《孔子和平獎》差唔多水平。今年三位邵逸夫獎得獎者，喺明知香港特首係一個完全冇人民授權、冇公信力嘅所謂政府首腦，再加上香港嘅人權狀況受到國際關注嘅情況下，仍然接受呢個獎項。實際上，三位得獎者係對於香港目前嘅情況視而不見。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z8HE77F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz8HE77F.jpg&h=8e6168d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要以香港人嘅身分，話俾呢三個得獎者知，佢哋今晚接受嘅，係嚟自中共邪惡政權下嘅傀儡所頒發嘅獎項。接受呢個獎，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等同於坐視香港政府嘅暴行，同埋背叛咗自己所屬國家嘅得來不易嘅民主自由價值。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今年三位邵逸夫得獎者如下：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>邵逸夫天文學獎得主：Edward C Stone</strong><br />\n所屬學術機構：California Institute of Technology (Caltech) 加州理工學院<br />\n電郵地址：ecs@srl.caltech.edu<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://directory.caltech.edu/personnel/ecs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdirectory.caltech.edu%2Fpersonnel%2Fecs&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=17552644\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://directory.caltech.edu/personnel/ecs</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>邵逸夫生命科學與醫學獎得主：Maria Jasin</strong><br />\n所屬學術機構：Weill Cornell Graduate School of Medical Sciences 康乃爾大學醫學院<br />\n電郵地址：m-jasin@ski.mskcc.org<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.mskcc.org/research/ski/labs/maria-jasin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mskcc.org%2Fresearch%2Fski%2Flabs%2Fmaria-jasin&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=5256a5a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mskcc.org/research/ski/labs/maria-jasin</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>邵逸夫數學科學獎得主：Michel Talagrand</strong><br />\n所屬學術機構：目前已退休<br />\n電郵地址：michel.talagrand@gmail.com<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://michel.talagrand.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmichel.talagrand.net%2F&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=8a6e8674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://michel.talagrand.net/</a><br />\n<br />\n咁多位手足，齊齊努力send 信過去，叫佢哋重新考慮係咪接受今年嘅邵逸夫獎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我地成功令至少一位得獎者放棄所頒獎項，將會喺國際學術界狠狠地兜巴車落特衰政府同條柒婆度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40e27d652a7c5d9effe63a0b6799813aa3609e2","tid":1594673,"uid":108725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:15:32.000Z","msg":"1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebbe8d8c2d4df9d841adcbe6cac07a9af2ed7d12","tid":1594673,"uid":108725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:15:53.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11a4d053228da428e8c2805633d07f550efb5a6","tid":1594673,"uid":108725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:16:03.000Z","msg":"3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8076a48587ab24c7cc79b22a13e6db497284b3d","tid":1594673,"uid":108725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:16:43.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1fc6085ddbc5d2ea5a21ec1619ef80a80bedf6a","tid":1594673,"uid":108725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:17:03.000Z","msg":"5<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor